Action.author: rickr
Action.body: Need at least full sdk logs and peer logs at least

Action.author: rickr
Action.body: The logs for fabric don't appear to be at debug level. The SDK logs also need to be at trace level. The SDK readme.md has some mention on setting trace. The SDK's docker-compose.yaml also has by default the full logging on the fabric side- if that does not work see fabric documentation.
